df3['Perc'] = df3['Freq'] / df3.groupby('App')['Freq'].transform('sum')

In [13]:
# Keeping dates only
df['Date'] = pd.to_datetime(df['Date&Time'], dayfirst = True, errors = 'coerce').dt.date
df['Date'] = pd.to_datetime(df['Date'], errors='coerce')
# Year and month
df['year'] = [d.year for d in df.Date]
df['month'] = df['Date'].dt.month
years = df['year'].unique()
In [14]:
# Period (year + month)
df['period'] = df['year'].astype(str) + '-' + df['month'].astype(str)
df['period'] = pd.to_datetime(df['period'], errors='coerce')
In [15]:
g = sns.relplot(
    data=df, x="period", y="Rating", col="Gender",
    hue="App", kind="line",
).set(xlabel=None)
g.fig.subplots_adjust(top=.8)
g.fig.suptitle('Rating Score Overtime')
